<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 00:00:08 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Fri, 11 Oct 2024 00:00:08 +0800</pubDate><item><title>速腾聚创第三季度激光雷达总销量约为13.86万台，同比增长134.9%</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/11812153.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p><span>10</span><span>月</span><span>10</span><span>日，速腾聚创公布</span><span>2024年第三季度业务进展概况。</span><span>第三季度，速腾聚创激光雷达总销量约为</span><span>138,600</span><span>台，同比增长</span><span>134.9%</span><span>，其中车载激光雷达销量约为</span><span>131,400</span><span>台，同比增长147.0%。</span><span>9</span><span>月，速腾聚创的激光雷达产品总销量约为</span><span>59,100</span><span>台，其中车载激光雷达产品销量约为</span><span>57,500</span><span>台，用于机器人及其他的激光雷达产品的销量约为</span><span>1,600台。<span><span>截至</span></span><span><span><span>2024</span></span></span><span><span>年</span></span><span><span><span>9</span></span></span><span><span>月</span></span><span><span><span>30</span></span></span><span><span>日，速腾聚创</span></span><span><span><span>2024</span></span></span><span><span>年激光雷达产品总销量约为</span></span><span><span><span>381,900</span></span></span><span><span>台，其中车载激光雷达产品销量约为</span></span><span><span><span>365,800</span></span></span><span><span>台，用于机器人及其他的激光雷达产品的销量约为</span></span><span><span><span>16,100</span></span></span><span><span>台。</span></span></span></p>
